    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily errands and weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and looks great, clearly showing it's been well-loved and looked after. If you're looking for a reliable car that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant features eight individual throttle bodies and a surgical 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a rapid-shifting M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The vehicle is mechanically robust, with critical preventative rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements already completed to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis retains its factory precision via the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system and a speed-sensitive variable M-differential lock. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, it remains a structurally rigid and performance-optimized example of the final naturally aspirated M-chassis.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean interior. Reliable performance. No mechanical issues. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that has been cared for with an eye for detail. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection will reveal the typical minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall handsome presence. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery remains supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and all power windows, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is tidy, reflecting a consistent maintenance schedule; the car starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and shifts through the gears without hesitation. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and tires have significant life remaining. This is a solid, honest car that offers a refined driving experience and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning motorist. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure optimal mechanical performance and structural integrity. Boasting a refined aesthetic and a detailed service history, it offers a sophisticated balance of longevity and value. We invite you to experience the superior road manners and build quality that define this model.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been well-loved and is still in great shape! It runs smoothly and looks fantastic inside and out. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love driving it as much as I have. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb mechanical example featuring the celebrated S54B32 inline-six power plant. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system to provide a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This chassis has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a valve lash adjustment, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains firm with crisp turn-in response, offering a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
